    Direct Known Subclasses:
    VotingDeskUI
    public abstract class Terminal
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    A simple abstract GUI utility class that is used to display a console like environment in the multicast server. This console allows members of the table to enqueue new users so they can go vote.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pedro Rodrigues, Miguel Rabuge
